data.description: Well-loved home in Cooper Colony Estates, Cooper City with no HOA!!! This 1875 SF Oasis features Four bedrooms, Two full and One-half bathroom in a split bedroom floor plan. Real wood kitchen cabinetry, granite countertops, and tile flooring throughout. New Roof in 2021 and Impact Windows for complete protection. Home has also been REPIPED and is backed by a 10-year warranty! (from the date of service). Bring your RV Boats, and any other rec vehicle. Both side yards have wide access. 30-amp electricity and water hook ups on one side. Carport in front and shed in back w/ impact windows and electricity. Walking/biking distance to CC elementary, Pioneer middle, and CC High.
